column5: Tornado Warning for the Smith Falls area.  Keep your heads up in Eastern Ontario boyz
We've had on and of clouds today. Here in Woody. Could use some rain. Keep safe if you are out there.
Eyes to the skies.  Stay safe all!!!
Interesting - My Dad and Step-Mom are in Rideau Ferry right now - just a few clicks down from Smiths Falls.

It's a few clicks UP from Smiths Falls Rich.. up stream anyhow!  Current radar looks more like Land o Lakes and Carleton Place are going to get the HEAVY rain at this point. Right across Moosebunks yard by the looks of it... hang tight Drew!
Had some interesting clouds develop but no damaging weather. Fingers crossed for now.
Fingers crossed for now.  I would never worry about it in Ottawa----chances are probably just slightly more that the Leaf winning the cup!!
